<div id="comment_status_64357772" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_64357772" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_64357772" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64357772" name="comment_link_64357772" href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23274696&amp;cid=64357772" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64357772)" >Faxing is better</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64357772" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64357772); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Okian+Warrior">Okian Warrior</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Okian+Warrior">( 537106 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64357772">		
		on Saturday March 30, 2024 @09:52PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23274696&amp;cid=64357772">#64357772</a>)
		<small><a href="http://www.okianwarrior.com/" title="http://www.okianwarrior.com/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
<a href="//slashdot.org/~Okian+Warrior/journal/" title="Tuesday May 16, 2023 @08:59PM" class="user_journal_display">Journal</a> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64357772"><p><div class="quote"><p><div class="quote"><p>Can Apps Turn Us Into Unpaid Lobbyists?</p></div><p>No, politicians weigh contacts by medium. The more effort put into the contact the more heavily weighted. Generated contacts, emails, texts, are considered to have near zero value. Now a handwritten letter sent via postal mail, that's an important contact.</p></div><p>Faxing is better. Powders and simple devices can be sent by letter, and politicians have to watch out for that.</p><p>Faxing means you're likely to be in a place that has a fax, ie a business, and if you put your thoughts on a letter with corporate logo then that's even better.</p><p>And yeah, faxing is very old school, but it's still used in a lot of down-to-earth places, the kind of grass-roots companies that politicians like to cultivate.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64357772">
